Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一座塔  -我需要在春天之前完工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A tower? -I need it completed by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有沒有考慮過 在外族中尋求合作伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you considered seeking partners outside the confines of our own race?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說你國王的提議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me about your King's proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來決定要不要呈報給我父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I can present it to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有所隱瞞 我是能感受到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd sense it if he were hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他感受到了有所隱瞞的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps he sensed that it was you who was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾島國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Island Kingdom of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在考慮推遲參加海洋試煉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking I might defer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等海洋試煉開始 那艘船啟航時 你必須在船上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the Sea Trial begins and that ship launches, you will be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想惹麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是南方大地的地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a map of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不僅提及了一個地點 還講述了一項計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It speaks not only of a place, but a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們將建立自己的領地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To create a realm of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方大地正處于嚴重危險之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Southlands are in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果索隆真的已經卷土重來 那么南方大地只會是個開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Sauron has indeed returned, the Southlands are but the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們這里有誰想活命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there are any of you here who want to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天日出時刻就一起前往精靈塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we make for the Elven tower at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他帶給阿達爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him to Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說古時候 索隆有很多個名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar! Sauron was said to have many names in days of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這就是其中一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps this is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同胞沒有國王 因為你就是國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people have no king, for you are him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有軍隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're still short an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些馬上就將改變\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is all about to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指環王：力量之戒\N第一季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這座王宮 我們每天 都會齊聚一堂 共同規劃島嶼的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this court, we gather daily to hammer out our island's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在“祝福新生兒”儀式中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at the Blessing of the Children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們歡聚一堂 共慶新生 他們長大后將見證這座島嶼的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we gather to welcome those who will live that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子就像沖破海面波濤的朝陽 擁有無限的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One as boundless as a sunrise over the rolling sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給她取了什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What name have you chosen for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳內爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳內爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你能夠擁有努門諾爾的力量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May Númenor's strength arise in thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿她的智慧指引你的腳步…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her wisdom guide thy steps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時我們的島嶼也需要“活動”一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes our island just needs a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是美好的一天 攝政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It is a perfect day, Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要先處理什么事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What business would you begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把那個精靈傳喚到了王宮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She summoned the Elf to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今早上的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈的同伴動手打了四個公會成員 而彌瑞爾卻請她喝茶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Elf's mate attacks four guildsmen, and Míriel has her up for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能傳喚精靈就是為了要懲罰她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably she called the Elf in to punish her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是向她討教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Or to ask her for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈在我們的女王耳邊扇陰風點鬼火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while the Elf whispers poison in our Queen's ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來替我們說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-who's speaking for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chancellor! Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向她問好 好嗎 你小聲點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send her my regards, will you? Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要來一份嗎 先生 來一份吧 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like one, sir? Come on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道您在忙很重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't realize you were in the middle of something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治國之道就是要事無巨細\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Statecraft is the art of attending to small matters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事必躬親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as diligently as grand ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你現在已經學到這一點了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should like to think you'd learned that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想辦法學著變聰明點兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was only trying to be clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野心不大的人才會只顧一味地變聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleverness is for men of small ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更希望你能有智慧 兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd much rather it if you were wise, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 出什么問題了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what seems to be the trouble, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在我們眼皮底下挑事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We may have a bit of a squall on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈的船悍然停在我們的海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf ships on our shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈工匠搶走你們的商業貿易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf workers taking your trades?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些工匠不需要睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Workers who don't sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會疲倦 也不會變老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't tire, don't age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說 女王要么是瞎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say, the Queen's either blind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是精靈的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or an Elf lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她父親一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Just like her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-精靈的舔狗  -精靈的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elf lover! -Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-精靈的舔狗  -精靈的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lover! Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個精靈現在就站在這里 她看到的會是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the Elf were here now, what would she see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是努門諾爾的鐵血男兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Men of Númenor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一群只會哭鬧的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or a gaggle of mewling children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是伊甸人的兒女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are sons and daughters of the Edain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是國王埃爾洛斯塔爾明雅圖爾的后代 他曾親自率軍打敗魔茍斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of Elros Tar-Minyatur, whose host conquered Morgoth himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在區區一個 坐船逃難的精靈就能威脅到我們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now one Elf, a castaway, could threaten us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所有人 低頭看看自己佩戴的公會徽章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look down, each of you, at the guild crests you bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是傳承自力量強大之手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heritage of mighty hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是偉大的祖先用雙手豎起了海堤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of men who laid the Sea Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造了象征我們文明勝利的 阿美尼洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who raised Armenelos, triumph of our civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在 區區一個精靈就能威脅我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now, one Elf could threaten us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我手上的老繭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For by the calluses on my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓精靈之手 永遠無法奪走努門諾爾王國的船舵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I swear that Elven hands will never take Númenor's helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾王國將一如既往地屬于人類\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She will remain, as always, a kingdom of Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請大家喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drinks all around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他熟知這座城市里每個人的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't a name in this city he doesn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總能說服人群改變想法 幾乎所有人都欠他人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a crowd he can't turn, a favor he isn't owed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想說“太讓人不爽了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was going to say "infuriating."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這酒產自美尼爾塔瑪的葡萄園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From vineyards near the Meneltarma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能讓你忘記煩惱 反正人們是這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposed to make you forget your troubles. Or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些甜蜜的煩惱都是我自己爭取來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My troubles have been too hard-won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個新來的學徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be the new apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凱門 你叫…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Kemen. And your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃雅瑞恩 趕緊交平面圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, E?rien. Plans, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹惱我了 精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You vex me, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你以禮相待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I welcome you as a guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻跑到我們鄉下去偷古老的卷軸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you gallop off to our countryside to steal ancient scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此同時 你那位來自中洲南方的 同伴還打了我們的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whilst your Southlander companion assaults our citizenry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的暴脾氣可以理解 畢竟他的人民正在死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is understandably quick to temper. His people are dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“他的人民”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"His people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你關在地牢里的那一位 并不是普通的鬧事者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe the man you hold in your dungeons is no common brawler,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是流亡在外 下落不明的南方大地王位繼承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the lost heir in exile to the throne of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看來埃蘭迪爾是一位東夷皇帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I suppose Elendil here is a Rh?nic emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也就是個小領主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a petty lord, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的人民散落各地 群龍無首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His people are scattered. Leaderless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有了你的支持 他們可能會 團結在他的旗幟之下 共同戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But with your backing they might unite behind his banner. And fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的“支持”是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean "backing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索隆曾經是你們人類的敵人 也是我們精靈的敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron was once your people's enemy, as much as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請求您完成這件未竟之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I call on you to finish the task left undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重建努門諾爾和精靈之間的聯盟…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To reforge the alliance between Númenor and Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我并肩作戰 拯救南方大地的人類\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And fight with me, to save the men of the Southlands
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免索隆將他們的土地據為己有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before Sauron claims their lands for his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個王宮之中 我們經常聽到許多提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this court we hear many proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的提案是幾周來 我聽過最令人驚訝、最具野心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I dare say yours is the most surprising and ambitious I've heard in weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 努門諾爾已經 選擇了另一條道路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nevertheless, Númenor has chosen another path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有人都是如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not all Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個來自南方大地的人 不管 他是國王還是木匠 都將面臨審判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}King or carpenter, the Southlander will face judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次會面結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This audience is ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我別無選擇了 只能要求另一場會面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I have little choice, but to ask for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求與努門諾爾真正的統治者會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One with Númenor's true ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你的父親 國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father, the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該說起你根本不了解的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not speak of matters you do not understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾 菲納芬之女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, daughter of Finarfin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該靠邊站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you should stand aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我才能 向真正有權答復我的人提出提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I might present my proposal to one who holds the authority to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾女士 夠了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Galadriel, that is quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什么說這番話 精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with what authority do you speak, Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That of your people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你就是個坐船逃難的精靈 想在風暴中抓住救命稻草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or are you a castaway, grasping for a handhold in a tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我內心就有一股強烈的風暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a tempest in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它把我刮到這座島上一定是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It swept me to this island for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你無法平息這股風暴 攝政王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it will not be quelled by you, Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜猜看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為在酒館斗毆進來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發表煽動性言論\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就快要成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've nearly made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a few more days,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能很榮幸地 稱呼你們所有人為船員了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have the pleasure of calling all of you shipmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拉 學員們 拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull now, cadets! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙爾杜…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拉 學員們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull now, cadets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好解釋一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explain yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官 這肯定搞錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, no, there must be some sort of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯 航海官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my fault, Sea-master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I let it slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條升降索 我見過你成功收放不下一百次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen you ease that halyard proper a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是故意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被踢出海上衛隊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're off the Sea Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們仨全部淘汰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“西部” “真正的努門諾爾”\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"The West"? "The real Númenor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你哥常掛在嘴邊的那些胡話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That garbage your brother used to spew, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為航海官只會開除我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought the sail-master would only dismiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對不起  你剛剛毀了我們倆的一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sorry? You just set our whole lives on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜壺在哪里 我要吐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's that chamber pot? I think I'm gonna be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和我爸談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will speak to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-給你們倆恢復原職 -用不著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Convince him to see that you're both reinstated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福給踢出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Leave it to you to get kicked out of something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更別說這個機會 本來也不是你自己贏來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you never earned in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-維藍迪爾… -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Valandil... -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打我能握住船槳起 我就一直想登上那艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since I was big enough to hold an oar, I wanted on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了一切準備 拼盡全力去爭取 而你又做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did everything I was supposed to do to earn it. And what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了念叨你死去的母親 你還做過什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you ever done but brood and blabber about your dead mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop it! Stop it! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是伊熙爾杜標志性的轉身走人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, same old Isil walking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙爾杜 你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isil! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去是留 有什么關系嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going, staying, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是真正的問題所在 這是無可爭辯的事實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real problem is him. And that's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬格羅特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Magrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿達爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿達爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無懼赴死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampak uglursha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無懼赴死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampak uglursha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的出生地在哪里…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where were you born,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝烈瑞安德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beleriand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河口附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the mouth of the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經去過那條河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went down that river once...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我還年輕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河岸上開滿了鼠尾草花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The banks were covered in sage blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿延好幾英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么奧克稱呼你為父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do the Orcs call you Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過很多謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been told many lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的謊言編得很真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some run so deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就連巖石和樹根都會相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even the rocks and roots now believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揭開謊言…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To untangle it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎需要創造一個新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would all but require the creation of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是只有神才能做到的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that is something only the gods can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是神 起碼…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I am no god. At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找那些在舊瞭望塔避難的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to the Men who have taken refuge in the old watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們捎個口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deliver to them a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What message?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵營已經滿了 大家盡可能找地方扎營\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The barracks are already full. Try and make camp where you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這些人是從哪來的  -羅爾巴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where's this lot from? -Iorbad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么從這兒到歐洛朱因 所有村莊的人都到齊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That makes it every village from here to Orodruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下這些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還得減少口糧配額\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll have to cut rations again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能減我的配額\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not cutting my rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是誰給你的決定權  -當然是每個決定來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who gave you the right to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這座瓦爾德雷格瞭望塔的人 其中也包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone who decided to come to this tower, Waldreg. Including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們會想出辦法的 -什么辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We'll find a way. -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道 -你能知道才怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I don't know. -Huh. Plain enough to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去瓦爾德雷格的地窖看看怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Waldreg's root cellar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們派一個小隊進鎮里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We send a small party into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等白天奧克數量比較少時 悄悄行動 把能拿走的東西迅速拿走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By day, when the Orcs are fewer, grab what we can, quick and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧克根本不會知道我們去過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll never even know we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備忽悠哪些倒霉蛋去干這事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What poor sod will you rope into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果其他人不愿意去 我自己去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll do it, if nobody else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not going down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先再次上山覓食 去召集獵人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll forage the hills again first. Gather the hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們去捕什么 幾只兔子嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what will they hunt? A few rabbits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只夠我們撐一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll feed us a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐過一天是一天 能多撐一天就應該心存感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it's another day. And let us be grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sick and tired
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著一切支離破碎卻無動于衷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of watching everything go to tatters and not doing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們已經在盡力而為了 -但我沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We are doing everything we can. -Well, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo. Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要么幫我 要么就是給我找麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can either help me or you can make it harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才就不應該聽你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have let you talk me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這么慫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be such a soft-belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅恩 那邊有小酒館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan, the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里邊可能有更多的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There might be more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 那個地方已經荒廢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, this place is deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童子血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Young blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你是從哪兒弄來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 是個小男孩  他手上有劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found it! It's a boy! He has the hilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩 他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A boy? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就躲在這附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's hiding here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 去向父親大人報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You! Send word to Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人 散開搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rest of you, fan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到他 誰也別想睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody sleeps till he's found.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.50,0:24:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈和矮人通力合作 真了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elves and Dwarves working together. Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被你言中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is everything you said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么 只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那里 有那么一瞬間 像極了你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a moment, standing there, you were the very image of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.08,0:25:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我都不知道你見過我父親 -當然了 見過很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't aware you'd ever met him. Of course, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.75,0:25:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擁有遠眺未來的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had that way of seeing far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 我記得有一次 他對我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know, I remember once, he said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.54,0:25:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“總有一天 我的未來都將掌握在我兒子手中”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one day, my future would be in his son's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.41,0:25:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說得很隨意 就好像是在說明天要下雨似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said it quite casually, as if one might speak of tomorrow's rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've... I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.41,0:25:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了 直到…直到此時此刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd forgotten that until... Till this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很奇怪嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.37,0:25:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 您今天似乎很不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seem unsettled today, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.87,0:25:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情在困擾您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What troubles you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.25,0:25:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我向自己保證過絕不提起 他畢竟是你朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I promised myself I wouldn't mention it. He's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.50,0:26:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要么是在躲避我 要么是在隱瞞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either he's avoiding me or he's... he's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問過他出工的團隊了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you try asking his work teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.50,0:26:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19個矮人我都問了 他們全都在找借口推辭我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All nineteen of them. They keep putting me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感覺近乎可疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One would almost think it suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.54,0:26:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在暗示 都林給自己找了個小女朋友嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting Durin's got himself a wee girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.87,0:26:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-夫人 你是都林的唯一 -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There is none other than you, milady. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.00,0:26:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會要他啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Who'd have him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.37,0:26:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 親石頭 拋光寶石 把金打磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich crone, kiss the stone Polish your gems and gold
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Ow! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.04,0:26:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格爾達 別打你弟弟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gerda, stop hitting your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們在玩敲門游戲 -好吧 別鬧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're playing the knocking game. -Well, knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.58,0:26:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去金色階梯找過了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you tried the Golden Stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.33,0:26:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者三門守衛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the Three-door Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.29,0:26:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.66,0:26:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些熊孩子把我的腦子都喊糊涂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These wee'ns are turning my mind to mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天去石英礦坑采礦去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was off to mine Quartz Chasm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.91,0:27:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 迪莎 沒有什么秘密值得用欺騙來掩飾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Disa, there is no secret worth concealing with deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.37,0:27:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我家指著鼻子說矮人不誠實\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calling a Dwarf dishonest in her own home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話火藥味頗濃啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a recipe for strong gravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.50,0:27:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果都林在采石英礦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Durin is mining quartz,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.16,0:27:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什么不帶著他的鑿斧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why would he leave without taking his chiseling axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你為什么 這么早就準備他愛吃的菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why would you prepare his favorite meal
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.41,0:27:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要兩天時間才能下降到那個礦坑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if he's gone to a chasm that takes two full days to descend to?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 親石頭 拋光寶石…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich crone, kiss the stone Polish your gems and gold
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格爾達 我警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gerda, I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.12,0:27:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林沒有帶斧頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin didn't bring his axe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.66,0:27:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他開采的石英不需要鑿 而是需要撬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because the quartz he's mining isn't chiseled. It is pried.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做鼴鼠尾燉菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am making mole-tail stew
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.79,0:27:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為趕在他回家之前 做好這道菜還需要花上一些時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it needs a wee while to set before he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.62,0:27:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對于像你這樣的外族來說 下降到礦坑可能需要幾天時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while it may take several days for an outsider, such as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但像我丈夫一樣的矮人攀登者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dwarven climbers like my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.75,0:28:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在幾個小時內就下降到石英礦坑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can make the descent to Quartz Chasm in just a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.45,0:28:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有什么想問的嗎 親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was there anything else you wanted to ask about, dearie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.37,0:28:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.70,0:28:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石英礦坑 編得不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quartz Chasm. Not bad. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就盼著他信了我 那個精靈可真不容易騙啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hope he believed me. He's not easily taken in, that Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.33,0:28:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不容易騙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的是 我未來的女王居然能把精靈忽悠信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lucky my future queen could convince a water rat to wear a mink coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.12,0:28:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了一個娶了你的好處 幸虧當年沒娶馬吉德魯斯特博林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more reason to count my blessings I married you, not Margid Rustborin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.58,0:28:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什么其他好處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what are the other reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.62,0:28:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜 我們最好還是小聲點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hush now. We better keep our pipes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.08,0:28:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的舊礦開采進展順利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're making good progress in the old mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.25,0:28:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確保他被護送離開…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made sure he was escorted out...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡影湖下面的舊礦場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The old mine below the Mirrormere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.00,0:29:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈 你迷路了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lost, Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我很清楚自己要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I know exactly where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.95,0:30:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 親石頭 拋光寶石 把金打磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Rich crone, kiss the stone. Polish your gems and gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.08,0:31:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈 你是來監視我的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Came to spy on me, Elf? -Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是 這是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真指望我相信你什么都不知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really expect me to believe you do not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.20,0:31:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是他派你來的真正原因嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That this was not the true reason he sent you here to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想要據為己有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want it for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.16,0:31:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林 想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin, want what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.41,0:31:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在乎那個洞穴里有什么東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care nothing for whatever is in that chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只在乎你 在乎這份友誼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do care for you, for this friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.41,0:31:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而秘密是會阻礙友誼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And secrets do not become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.12,0:31:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么大場面是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is the meaning of all this? Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得發誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.50,0:31:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向山起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hand to mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠不會將我要告訴你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll never breathe so much as a whisper
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴其他生靈 哪怕是輕聲細語也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of what I'm about to tell you to another living soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.54,0:32:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人的記仇能力比精靈的記憶力還強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dwarven anger outlives even Elven memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你違背誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Break your promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.70,0:32:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊石頭的力量 必將令你和你的親人陷入悲傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the power of this stone will doom you and your kin to sorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.54,0:32:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至你們活在中洲的最后一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to your last day on this Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.04,0:32:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢這樣發誓嗎 埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you swear it, Elrond?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以我父親 水手埃雅仁迪爾的名義起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear on the memory of my father, E?rendil the Mariner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里告訴我的任何事情 都將止于我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you tell me here will end in my ears alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.62,0:32:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莎在一次例行的金礦搜尋中 發現了這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disa detected it during a routine gold-seaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.75,0:32:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一種新礦石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A new ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.29,0:33:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比絲輕 比鐵硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lighter than silk, harder than iron,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.58,0:33:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用作武器 它比我們最引以為豪的兵刃還要鋒利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as weaponry, it would best our proudest blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.66,0:33:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為實物 它可能比黃金還珍貴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As specie, it might be dearer than gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它反射光線的方式很奇特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is strange how it catches the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像礦石內部就在發光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost seems lit from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.79,0:33:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說 這可能是我們矮人新時代的開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, this could be the beginning of a new era for our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.00,0:33:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量、繁榮…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength, prosperity...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.75,0:33:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什么要藏著掖著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why all the secrecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.12,0:33:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不慶祝一番呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not celebrate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.04,0:33:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種礦的開采非常危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's perilous to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.58,0:33:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親打著謹慎的名義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father has restricted our every efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處處限制我們開采\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the name of caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.54,0:33:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看看嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么稱呼這種神奇的礦石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you call this miracle ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.29,0:33:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的語言里 叫“灰色的閃光”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In our tongue, "gray glitter."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.37,0:33:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你們的話 可能叫什么“米銀”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In yours, something like mith-raud.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.66,0:34:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 是秘銀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. It would be... mithril.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.54,0:34:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你遠道而來 就只為了埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you really did come all this way just for Eregion?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.04,0:34:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這里是因為 20年不見老朋友一面 太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came because 20 years is far too long to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我這個精靈都覺得久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even for an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.66,0:34:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.54,0:34:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象征著我們的友誼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.45,0:34:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Durin! Durin! Durin, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.95,0:34:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有四個矮人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's four Dwarves down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.66,0:34:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.33,0:35:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃雅瑞恩 掃地 洗高腳杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E?rien, floors and goblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.66,0:35:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.87,0:35:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 說真的 沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right. It's all right. It's... It's... It's all right, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你只擅長制圖呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here I thought your talents ended at draftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.83,0:35:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦擦洗洗會讓人更加靈巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scrubbing is good for dexterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.70,0:35:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長是這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or so the guild master says.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.75,0:35:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這樣如何  我擦地板 你洗高腳杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how about this? I'll do the floors, you do the goblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.79,0:35:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰擦得慢 晚餐錢就由誰來付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the last one to finish pays for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.75,0:35:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不和不認識的年輕男士約會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not in the habit of going off with strange young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.83,0:35:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明智 如果我看到 哪個男士舉止怪異 立馬告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very wise. If I see any, you'll be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.25,0:36:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡管我很佩服你 每次遇到困難都會沖鋒陷陣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As much as I admire your habit of charging at every obstacle in your path,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一匹全速奔跑的小馬…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like a colt in full gallop...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.58,0:36:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你有沒有想過 你不是在和食人妖或奧克作斗爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has it ever occurred to you that you're not battling trolls or Orcs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.91,0:36:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是和人類\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.37,0:36:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的要給我兵法方面的建議嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you really about to advise me in the art of war?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.12,0:36:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't dare. But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.79,0:36:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的王宮 和你平日的戰場并不相同 沒錯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The queen's court isn't exactly your usual battlefield, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.08,0:36:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.66,0:36:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下 依我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In an instance like this, it seems to me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.75,0:36:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好要弄清楚對手最害怕的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you'd do well to identify what it is that your opponent most fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-然后利用這一點  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-And exploit it? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.08,0:36:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要給他們一種掌控這種恐懼的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give them a means of mastering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.79,0:37:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就可以掌控對手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that you can master them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.45,0:37:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以按照你的標準 我在這個牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So by your standards, I'm in this cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我還沒有找出 女王最害怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I've yet to identify what the queen most fears?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只達到了低標準 但沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My very low standards. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.95,0:37:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只見了女王一小會兒 看來你已經確定了她最害怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I suppose you did, having met her for all of a few moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.75,0:37:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會面期間 你索要了船只 侮辱了她的人民、違抗了她的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During which you managed to demand a ship, insult her people, defy her orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些都沒有讓她情緒起伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}none of which quickened her pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.33,0:37:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 突然間 她把你扔進了牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, all of a sudden, she throws you in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.12,0:37:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.33,0:37:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請求她為你的人民而戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked her to fight for your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這不是引起她憤怒的原因吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that wasn't what provoked her anger, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求和她父親會面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I demanded to speak with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.00,0:37:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年來 沒有人見過的 塔中的國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The king in the tower, whom no one has seen in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.87,0:37:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你知道停止奔跑 給自己 一點時間思考 會發生什么了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See what happens when you stop galloping and you give yourself a moment to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.54,0:37:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再把我比作一匹馬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cease comparing me to a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.25,0:37:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 那你別再說服我離開這座島了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cease trying to convince me to leave this island an you have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.20,0:37:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意 精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salutations, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.70,0:37:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝政女王做出了決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen Regent has rendered her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.37,0:38:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 你將在武裝護送下 被運回精靈的領地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are to be shipped back to the Elves under armed escort. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.58,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.91,0:38:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不建議你這樣做 -我不能讓她就這樣離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I wouldn't advise that. -I can't very well let her leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果知道她要去哪里的話 你肯定會放她走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You could. If you knew exactly where she was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.83,0:39:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這上面干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛跟人約會吃飯去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.75,0:39:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.00,0:39:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的制服呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是辭職不當學員了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Resigned from the cadets, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.33,0:39:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 比這更糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.83,0:39:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被開除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got dismissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害得我們幾個都被開除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got us all dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.83,0:39:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isil...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.79,0:39:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你贏了 現在你可以去西部了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you've won. Now you can go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毀了朋友們的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just ruined my friends' lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.91,0:39:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞辱了家門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shamed our family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.29,0:39:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不配去西部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't deserve to go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.66,0:39:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 父親不會讓我帶走貝雷克的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Plus, Father won't let me take Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.04,0:39:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個精靈 她逃出來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the Elf! She's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.25,0:39:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細搜查每一個小巷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Search every alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.33,0:40:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 陛下 打擾了 但是我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologies, Your Majesty, for the intrusion. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經沒法再回應了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He no longer answers to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我會來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you know I would come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.95,0:40:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有一支駐軍等著護送你上船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A garrison of troops awaits outside to escort you to your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放聰明點 自己主動離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would be wise to go willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.41,0:40:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌瑞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.00,0:40:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌瑞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.75,0:41:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.83,0:41:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 父親 我在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It's all right, Father. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.08,0:41:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.04,0:41:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是這個情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.45,0:41:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒幾個人知道 他身體惡化到了這種地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few know the full extent of his decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望繼續瞞著所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should like to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.79,0:41:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們倆之間就開誠布公吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it is time for truth between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.00,0:41:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親之前忠于精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father was loyal to the Elvish ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.62,0:41:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么不愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.87,0:41:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.45,0:41:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親以前對他的信念總是很克制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father was always restrained in his beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.25,0:41:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在他加冕之后 情況發生了變化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But after his coronation, something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.25,0:41:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他開始變得很強硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He became strident,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.45,0:41:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣稱我們激怒了維拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}proclaiming that we'd provoked the anger of the Valar,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣稱我們必須悔改 回歸往日的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and must repent, and return to the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.50,0:42:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有民眾對此感到不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當我父親宣布 計劃與精靈再續友好關系時…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when he announced plans to renew relations with the Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民眾造反了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people rebelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.12,0:42:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損失慘重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.70,0:42:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被選中接替他的統治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was chosen to rule in his stead,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.20,0:42:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承諾要平息動亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a promise to quell the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我繼位的第一個晚上 等努門諾爾人都睡著了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that first night, as all Númenor slept,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.91,0:42:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親把我帶到了這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.95,0:42:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕藍提爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Palantír.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.20,0:42:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有七顆真知晶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven Seeing Stones there once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.33,0:42:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他六顆丟的丟 藏的藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other six either lost or hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.91,0:42:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一顆傳給了我父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one was passed to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.79,0:42:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有一個秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with it, a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.58,0:42:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手放在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Place your hand upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.58,0:42:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得警告你… -我以前觸摸過帕藍提爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}-I must warn you... -I have touched palantíri before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.75,0:42:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒有碰過這一顆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you have not touched this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.87,0:43:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才看到的是努門諾爾的未來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is Númenor's future you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.83,0:43:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕藍提爾能呈現出很多異象\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Palantíri show many visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.75,0:43:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些異象永遠不會發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some that will never come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.83,0:43:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經發生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has already come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打你來到這里 這個異象就開始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vision begins with your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我會導致努門諾爾的覆滅嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you believe I will bring about Númenor's downfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.41,0:43:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有努門諾爾才能讓自己覆滅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only Númenor can bring about her downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.25,0:43:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個恩德圓滿的日子 維拉將這座島嶼賜予了我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Valar gifted us this isle in a day of virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若我們調頭走向黑暗 那他們大可把這座島嶼收回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can take it away should we turn to the paths of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.87,0:44:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的恩德 就是你祖先對精靈的忠誠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The virtue you speak of was your ancestors' loyalty to the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.91,0:44:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親對此深信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father believed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.91,0:44:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他帶領的路差點讓我們毀于一旦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His path nearly destroyed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什么 明天我要宣布你已經走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why, tomorrow, I will announce that you are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.79,0:44:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時宣布這場危機結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this crisis ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.20,0:44:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對中洲 正在崛起的邪惡勢力放任不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the evil rising in Middle-earth is left unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.25,0:44:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它必然擴散 毀滅我們所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it will spread and take us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.41,0:44:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意避免這場戰爭 可能恰恰就是導致你們覆滅的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Avoiding this war may be the very thing that brings about your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.91,0:44:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會質疑諸神 這就是我最后的決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not second-guess the gods. My decision is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.16,0:44:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出于恐懼而做的決定吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A decision based in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.79,0:44:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道作為唯一知情的人 是什么樣的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what it is to be the only one,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.37,0:44:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only one who sees,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己才知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.04,0:44:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們倆 都不必再獨自承擔這個負擔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps neither of us have to bear that burden alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.25,0:44:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了 彌瑞爾 不要選擇恐懼的那條道路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I beg of you, Míriel, choose not the path of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選擇充滿信念的那條路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我站在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.12,0:45:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓努門諾爾再次與精靈并肩作戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let Númenor fight alongside the Elves once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.95,0:45:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心可以遵從信念 加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faith may bind one heart, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.16,0:45:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要讓一個王國只依靠信念 實在是有點靠不住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it is too fine a thread from which to hang a kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.16,0:45:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹林都是光禿禿的 動物也都四散逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woods are all bare. Animals are all fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.16,0:45:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的孩子比我們原以為的更聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems your boy had more sense than we allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.83,0:45:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門口有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There's someone at the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.50,0:45:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.83,0:45:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-別擋路 退后  -讓這小伙子過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Move out of the way. Stand back! -Let the lad through!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.37,0:45:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多吃的 慢點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's plenty. Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.20,0:45:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅恩 希奧在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan! Where's Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.54,0:45:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才說會緊跟著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he'd be right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.20,0:46:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好餓  -別推了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm so hungry! -Stop pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.54,0:46:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她推我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She pushed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.37,0:46:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把每個角落都檢查過了 他沒回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've turned over every stone. He ain't back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.33,0:46:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.70,0:46:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.45,0:46:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.54,0:46:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.29,0:46:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細搜查 不留死角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找不到他 老大會活剝了我們的皮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boss will skin us alive if we don't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.37,0:46:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老大最先把他弄丟的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boss is the one who lost him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.25,0:46:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到他的氣味了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Izm?mbogh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.45,0:46:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.50,0:46:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kishdibatoth! Kishdibatoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.29,0:47:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kishdibatoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.33,0:47:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他找出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.00,0:47:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.91,0:47:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊 看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Over there! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鮮肉 你急著要跑去哪兒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going somewhere, young blood, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.16,0:48:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把劍在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.33,0:48:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.41,0:48:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪兒弄到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where have you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.66,0:48:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍掉你一只手臂 看你開不開口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe losing your arm will loosen your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.04,0:48:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Swiftly, lad. -Over there! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.33,0:48:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.79,0:49:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.29,0:49:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.95,0:49:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.83,0:49:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 去空地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run! Get to the clearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.12,0:52:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.87,0:52:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在懇求巖石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a plea to the rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.58,0:52:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請它保佑礦工還有呼吸 能夠安全逃生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to release the bodies of the miners with breath still inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.00,0:52:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想 要不是你去礦井找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot stop thinking that if you'd not gone down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.12,0:52:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林很有可能會在那個豎井里…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin might have been in that shaft when it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.37,0:52:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.16,0:52:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我騙了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.75,0:52:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告訴我也是為了都林好 我們只要記住這個就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were faithful to my friend. -That is all we need remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.54,0:52:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們剛把最后一名礦工拖了出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just pulled out the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著 他們都活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Alive. All of them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.33,0:52:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親肯定松了一口氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father must be so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.33,0:52:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把礦井關停了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整條礦脈都要被封死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole vein is to be sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.20,0:52:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-整條礦脈  -一整條\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The whole vein? -All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.04,0:53:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他點時間嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脾氣再大 氣也總會消的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the hottest coals eventually cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.08,0:53:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但有時候 我倒是希望他一直在氣頭上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but sometimes I wish they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.75,0:53:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我真希望 能告訴父親我對他的真實看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes I wish I could tell him exactly what I think of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.37,0:53:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再也不和那個糟老頭子說話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never trade words with the old goat again!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.25,0:53:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親曾經獨自航行到維林諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father single-handedly sailed to Valinor,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.25,0:53:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說服維拉加入戰爭 并成功消滅魔茍斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and convinced the Valar to join the war and vanquish Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.16,0:53:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事跡如此偉大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So great were his deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.29,0:53:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于維拉 把他帶到了這個世界的邊界之外…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the Valar lifted him beyond the bounds of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.62,0:54:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠帶著暮色之星劃過天空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To forever carry the Evening Star across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.66,0:54:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么多年來 每到深夜 我都會抬頭看看它…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For many years, at day's end, I would look up at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.16,0:54:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道如果他在看著我 他會怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wondering what might he think if he were watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.12,0:54:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會為我在他的傳承之上 取得的成就而感到驕傲嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would he be proud of what I've accomplished with his legacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.70,0:54:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會因為我未能達到 他的種種期望而對我感到失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or disappointed by the countless ways I'd failed to live up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.25,0:54:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但后來有一天晚上 我突然想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then, one night, it struck me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.12,0:54:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能聽到他的評價 無論好壞 我都能心滿意足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I would be only too happy to hear any judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.16,0:54:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只求獲得再次與父親說話的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so long as it granted me the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.50,0:54:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有一次也好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to have but one more conversation with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.83,0:54:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪費你和父親所剩不多的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not waste what time you have left with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.66,0:55:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德 我期待你能解答一些問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond, I was hopeful you might be able to settle something.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.66,0:55:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我老公是怎么認識的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it that you and my husband met?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.25,0:55:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你 我把他從山嶺食人妖手中救了出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, I saved him from a hill-troll.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.91,0:55:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是兩個山嶺食人妖哦 -兩個 對 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Two of 'em. -Two of 'em. Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.79,0:55:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在問埃爾隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was asking Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.75,0:55:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那恐怕我別無選擇 只能糾正一下你丈夫的描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I fear I have no choice but to amend your husband's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.83,0:55:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時有三個山嶺食人妖 而且是我救的他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were three trolls. And it was I who saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.66,0:55:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不照照鏡子看看自己長什么樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't remember your face if you were gazing in a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.16,0:55:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我在森林里遇見他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I came upon him in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.00,0:55:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在躲避山嶺食人妖的槌擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he was in the midst of dodging their mallet blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.54,0:55:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在那里嚎啕大哭什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wailing and screaming and such. 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.29,0:55:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那是戰場的吶喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It was a battle cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.58,0:55:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的喊叫聲非常尖銳 我當時還以為是個小孩 我拿著弓…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The screams were so high-pitched, I thought it was a child. So I took up my bow...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.33,0:55:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是一把劍 -是一把弓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Uh, it was a sword. -It was a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 是一把劍  -不管怎么樣…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nah! It was a sword! -Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.50,0:55:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我 父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.54,0:55:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太過驕傲、固執 我錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was proud and stubborn and I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.66,0:55:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能看我一眼嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you not even look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們矮人相信…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.70,0:56:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當新的矮人國王加冕時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That when a new Dwarf-king is crowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.66,0:56:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有祖先的聲音都會匯集在他心頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the voices of all his forebearers flow into him,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.41,0:56:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與他分享前輩們的經驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sharing with him their counsel
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.58,0:56:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.75,0:56:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還有錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Even their mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.08,0:56:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.58,0:56:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必等到那一天 就能聽到我的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need not wait for that day to hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.58,0:56:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 兒子 我永遠和你在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For, ever am I with you, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.83,0:57:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我非常憤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even in anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.87,0:57:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的時候 我基本上一直在發怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes, in anger most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.45,0:57:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒什么需要我原諒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德邀請我明天和他一起去林頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond has invited me to go with him to Lindon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.29,0:57:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該接受嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall I accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.54,0:57:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德保證 吉爾加拉德派他來這里并沒有惡意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond has been very convincing in his assurances
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.45,0:57:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾隆德的話讓人非常信服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Gil-galad bore no ill intent when he sent him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.87,0:57:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 的確是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye. He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.29,0:57:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但直覺是一種強有力的輔助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But intuition's a powerful tonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.04,0:57:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的直覺如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does yours tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.79,0:57:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺事有蹊蹺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something more at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.91,0:58:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的 兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.04,0:58:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.04,0:58:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去林頓吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.79,0:58:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.91,0:58:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.00,0:58:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.95,0:58:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的指揮官讓我帶回來一條口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a message. From the one who commands our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.08,0:58:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人民要想保全性命 必須放棄這些土地的所有權…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That your people may live if you forsake all claim to these lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.66,0:58:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并向他宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And swear fealty to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.50,0:58:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們拒絕呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if we refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.41,0:58:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他就會來歐斯提力斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming for Ostirith.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.04,0:59:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.87,0:59:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說 你的所做作為 配得上喝一口好酒作為獎賞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, you deserve a nip of mash after what you done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.50,0:59:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 拿著吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.58,0:59:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你從我谷倉里 拿走了那把劍一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like you took that hilt from me barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.25,0:59:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你說什么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... I don't know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.54,1:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝了 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come off it, lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.75,1:00:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我說的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know of what I speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.08,1:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什么嗎 這并不是劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what it is? It is no sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.16,1:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是一種力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a power.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.29,1:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他的主人親手為我們的祖先打造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fashioned for our ancestors by his master's own hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.29,1:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個漂亮的仆人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A beautiful servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.91,1:00:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經不知所蹤 但終將歸來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He who was lost, but shall return.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.04,1:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 你聽說過他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of him, lad?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.75,1:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過索隆嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.91,1:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定在天上看到過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have seen it in the skies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.87,1:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾周前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few weeks back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.54,1:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星隕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The starfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.87,1:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這意味著他的時間快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means his time is near.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.83,1:00:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 這需要你和我共同做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it is to you and me, lad, to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.75,1:00:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.20,1:00:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hush now, lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.41,1:01:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保存好體力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You save your strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.58,1:01:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要發生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.62,1:01:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會非常消耗體力的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.83,1:01:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord-father...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.12,1:01:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.37,1:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座塔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.45,1:01:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.79,1:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人民會感到寬慰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people will be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.37,1:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很快就會聚集在王宮里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will be gathering soon in the court,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.54,1:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在廣場上 聆聽你的宣告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and in the plaza, to hear your announcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.20,1:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就別讓他們久等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we ought not to keep them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.79,1:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠貞派相信 白樹的花瓣落下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The faithful believe that when the petals of the White Tree fall
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.20,1:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的預兆…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it is no idle thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.08,1:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是維拉的眼淚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the very tears of the Valar themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.37,1:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮活地提醒著我們 他們時刻緊盯我們 審判我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a living reminder that their eyes and their judgment are ever upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.45,1:04:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 人類命運迎來了 一個決定性的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a fateful hour in the destinies of men.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.54,1:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個審判的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An hour of judgment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.00,1:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之中 我們所有人、每個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in which each of us, every one,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.00,1:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須決定自己將要成為誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}must decide who we shall be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.20,1:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心會像 小島周圍的石像一樣鐵石心腸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are our hearts become as the statues that surround our isle?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.95,1:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會同石像雕刻的 英雄一般充滿滿腔熱忱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or do they yet beat with the blood of the heroes that carved them?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.16,1:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的勇氣 是否只存在于父輩的墳墓之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is our valor confined to the graves of our slumbering fathers?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.50,1:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or is it here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.79,1:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們眾人之中…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}amongst us even now...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.00,1:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待隨著太陽升起而迸發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waiting to burst forth as the rising Sun?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.45,1:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們去面對 連我自己都不敢直面的危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would neither command, nor invite you to any danger I myself would not face.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.54,1:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我決定親自護送精靈返回中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so, I've decided to personally escort the Elf back to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.62,1:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援助被圍困在南方大地的凡人同胞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To aid our mortal brethren who are now besieged in the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.16,1:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王已經明確表明意圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your queen has laid bare her intent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.29,1:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的船隊將在十天后啟程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our ships will depart in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.70,1:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠征軍將由努門諾爾全境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The expeditionary force will be made up of brave sons and daughters
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.33,1:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的兒女組成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from across fair Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.37,1:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰愿意真心實意 保護我們的攝政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is willing to commit themselves to our Queen Regent's protection?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.83,1:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請向前一步讓大家看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step forward and make yourself known.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.16,1:06:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.91,1:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.12,1:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.66,1:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.91,1:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve!
